Installation:

No significative hint about installing, I mean no one came
from my code.

Rember you need pyserial from http://pyserial.sourceforge.net/


1.  BUILDING

No building neccessary

2.  INSTALLATION

Type 'make install' (as root if needed) to install the executables
under '/usr/local/bin' or whathever was specified as PREFIX into
Makefile.

3.  UNINSTALLATION

Type 'make uninstall' (as root if needed) to remove executables
installed.
